{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/ber4444/kmp-videos/pulls/38","id":4094854761,"node_id":"PR_kwDOEv28is70EoZp","html_url":"https://github.com/ber4444/kmp-videos/pull/38","diff_url":"https://github.com/ber4444/kmp-videos/pull/38.diff","patch_url":"https://github.com/ber4444/kmp-videos/pull/38.patch","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/ber4444/kmp-videos/issues/38","commits_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/ber4444/kmp-videos/pulls/38/commits","review_comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/ber4444/kmp-videos/pulls/38/comments","review_comment_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/ber4444/kmp-videos/pulls/comments{/number}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/ber4444/kmp-videos/issues/38/comments","statuses_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/ber4444/kmp-videos/statuses/f944c1f0f096af73a7ad0cdcd14ae268ee8f1943","number":38,"state":"open","locked":false,"title":"feat: Implement Cross-Platform Parity and Whisper AI Captions","user":{"login":"ber4444","id":205867,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjIwNTg2Nw==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/205867?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/ber4444","html_url":"https://github.com/ber4444","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ber4444/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ber4444/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ber4444/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ber4444/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ber4444/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ber4444/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ber4444/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ber4444/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ber4444/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"body":"## High-Level Summary of Features\n\nThis PR implements extensive cross-platform parity improvements across Android, iOS, and Wasm targets, and fundamentally upgrades our on-device AI transcription engine to use Whisper C++.\n\n### Cross-Platform Parity\n- **Web Navigation:** Wasm target now sports a fully functional browser-based back navigation stack.\n- **Unified Login UX:** A beautiful, responsive glassmorphism aesthetic is now applied uniformly across the login screens of all platforms (Android, iOS, Web).\n- **iOS Thumbnail Engine:** iOS now extracts scrubbing preview thumbnails natively via `AVAssetImageGenerator` utilizing hardware acceleration.\n- **iOS Offline HLS:** iOS now robustly downloads background HLS streams using native `AVAssetDownloadURLSession`, matching Android's capability.\n- **Robust MediaKit Probing:** Redesigned `EventCatalog` to handle Master and Media playlist parallel probing sequentially and safely for all targets.\n\n### AI Captions (Whisper Integration)\n- **Engine Migration:** The live caption generation has been fully migrated from Vosk to **Whisper C++** natively integrated via Android NDK for blazing fast, on-device transcription!\n- **Mobile-Optimized Models:** Uses the `ggml-base.en` Whisper model to guarantee fluid, real-time transcription latency on mobile CPUs (avoiding the silent hangs associated with massive models like large-v3-turbo).\n- **Dynamic UX:** The Caption toggle button now provides real-time, percentage-based model download progress directly in the player UI!\n","labels":[],"milestone":null,"active_lock_reason":null,"created_at":"2026-07-20T21:54:09Z","updated_at":"2026-07-20T23:31:25Z","closed_at":null,"merged_at":null,"merge_commit_sha":"7c6ede7e8a7a3a0f0d9ea92fa031642bc9561cd9","assignee":null,"assignees":[],"requested_reviewers":[],"requested_teams":[],"head":{"label":"ber4444:feature/platform-parity","ref":"feature/platform-parity","repo":{"id":318618762,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnkzMTg2MTg3NjI=","name":"kmp-videos","full_name":"ber4444/kmp-videos","owner":{"login":"ber4444","id":205867,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjIwNTg2